Freezing Trap

Explosive Trap

Tar Trap

Enemies moving through the tar have a chance to be rooted in place for 4 sec.



Steel Trap

Your Steel Trap also deals an immediate 71,740 Bleed damage when triggered.



Caltrops

Increases Caltrops damage by 50%.
